item.title: CVE-2024-34683|2024-08-02T02:59:22.208Z -- sap_se -- sap%20document%20builder
item.description: An authenticated attacker can upload malicious file to SAP Document Builder service. When the victim accesses this file, the attacker is allowed to access, modify, or make the related information unavailable in the victim’s browser.
